ng about which side would be preferred which has a lot more to do with the presentation of the conflict than any psychological I think there is no doubt that despite the fact we intervened in Somalia the level of attention devoted to there was considerably less than what is devoted to Bosnia if the newspapers and tv news I see are any Dave